{"tid":1883280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3持刀賊劫旺角超市　掠走60條卷裝廁紙","createTime":"2020-02-16T23:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T04:21:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"184d83d863ca68160086af7124cc9a1208125284","tid":1883280,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4014143/org/28ad260f677a26c6455f9bac3a35baef.jpg/k6ITe2QL_uf316Dc20f2uHeWOUI6RXsTP7XELBW1xCw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4014143%2Forg%2F28ad260f677a26c6455f9bac3a35baef.jpg%2Fk6ITe2QL_uf316Dc20f2uHeWOUI6RXsTP7XELBW1xCw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=0cf46494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒（武漢肺炎）令全港人心惶惶，市面上多種清潔用品連日來供不應求，今早（17日）更驚現廁紙劫案。早上約6時05分，送貨工人將多條卷裝廁紙，送抵旺角道97號地下的一間超級市場，並將貨物置放於店外看管。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，超市在早上7時才營業，當貨物運抵約15分鐘後，突有3名戴帽及口罩的男子撲出，其中1人手持兩把利刀，指嚇送貨男工人，並呼喝他「坐喺度唔好郁！」，隨即將60條卷裝廁紙，放入一輛超市手推車內，然後「連紙帶車」，沿洗衣街往太子方向逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警方事後封鎖現場調查，並將仍置放在店外的廁紙圍封，人員亦在附近兜截，未幾在約10米外洗衣街與旺角道交界，發現一個懷疑屬於匪徒的行李篋。警方將案件列作「行劫」處理，現正追緝賊人歸案。現場所見，超市門外放有逾百排卷裝廁紙，另外亦有食用油及餅乾等。"},{"pid":"b8f27688da3330b4ac15cb02f9286f4f1e29313a","tid":1883280,"uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T23:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4014147/org/1aabb390072e8fe240f41367f93bb549.jpg/M-gklUJ_tLF9k8XjJn51wD72s_qTEicvTcsn-WfLJ_k?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4014147%2Forg%2F1aabb390072e8fe240f41367f93bb549.jpg%2FM-gklUJ_tLF9k8XjJn51wD72s_qTEicvTcsn-WfLJ_k%3Fv%3Dw640&h=bbfbef3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4014145/org/17e7db05d22ff406b7bd936d59c73659.jpg/kbCh1yPbXqPKCNtQc3ZsezkqZVxG1AUYu28a55FvGuc?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4014145%2Forg%2F17e7